# Combinatorial Theory of Riemann Surfaces

This module collects the combinatorial (ribbon graph) aspects of
Riemann surface theory:

- Ribbon graphs and their topology
- Cell decomposition of Teichmüller space
- Kontsevich intersection theory
- Witten-Kontsevich theorem

These tools are essential for:
1. Computing Weil-Petersson volumes (Mirzakhani)
2. Intersection numbers on M̄_{g,n}
3. Integration over moduli space via cell decomposition
